Linux - Automatic Installation (One-liner)

Step 1: Select the collector packaging mode.
Copy to clipboard
curl -Lo setup.sh https://github.com/instana/instana-otel-collector/releases/latest/download/instana-collector-installer-latest.sh && chmod +x setup.sh && ./setup.sh -a qUMhYJxjSv6uZh2SyqTEnw -e agent.apps.itz-z4fxgh.infra01-lb.fra02.techzone.ibm.com:4317 -H agent.apps.itz-z4fxgh.infra01-lb.fra02.techzone.ibm.com:4318
Step 2: Run the OpenTelemetry deployment code.
Copy to clipboard
1---
2receivers:
3  otlp:
4    protocols:
5      grpc:
6        endpoint: localhost:24317 # By default only host system has access
7  filelog:
8    include: ["/var/log/*.log"]
9    include_file_path: true
Optional: After your collector deploys successfully, you can view it on the infrastructure map.
